Revision history for Perl extension Authen::Simple

0.5 2006-01-14 00:00
    - Removed cache and callback options from Authen::Simple::Adapter. Same 
      functionality is provided by Authen::Simple::Cache and Authen::Simple::Callback.
    - Added Authen::Simple::Base and Authen::Simple::Decorator
    - Log a debug message and return false if authenticate was called with 
      a undefined username or password.

0.4 2006-01-13 00:00
    - Documented supported passoword formats
    - Added reference to Authen::Simple::DBI and Authen::Simple::CDBI

0.3 2006-01-12 00:00
    - Added Authen::Simple::Password
    - Added reference to Authen::Simple::NIS

0.2 2006-01-04 00:00
    - Added tests

0.1 2006-01-03 00:00
    - First release
